item.title: By: Foton
item.dc:creator: Foton
item.description:
ffs, think I just had kick the database. That's goofy as hell.
EDIT: For any other WP users that have a similar feed problem when upgrading, either a new post and comment, or editing previously-posted ones, will fix the feeds. Other than that, was an easy, troublefree upgrade.
EDIT2: Above only fixes feeds as long as there is activity w/i the last 24 hours. Permanent fix is outlined <a href="http://fernando.dubtribe.com/archives/2005/05/10/solution-to-wp151-rss-errors/">here</a>.
